data.description: Lovely Ranch in desirable area, near schools and parks. Freshly painted exterior of home and garage. Lots of painting on the interior as well. Nice layout with 3 bedrooms, large living room, beautifully updated bath and kitchen with new counters. Functional lower level finished room with another full bath. New central air in 2023!! Attached screened in patio and the nice sized backyard are ready for your family parties!!!
